name: Twinkle Stone
shortDescription:
Users can register, login or logout from the website
 2.Users can place order to his/her MyOrder section of the user dashboard.Users can remove order to his/her MyOrder section of the user dashboard
.Users can add a review to that product that he/she brought.Users have purchased the history analytics section in the user dashboard which is static.
There is an admin panel where admin can manage both users and products.Admin can add or remove any product
.Only admin can make another user admin.Admin can manage products
.Admin also can change status from pending to approve which will see user as shipped. Admin can cancel order
.Admin also have sales analytics section in the admin dashboard which is static.Admin have featured info section in the admin dashboard. Product price will calculate automatically.Firebase hoisting
Technology: React.js, REST API,Redux, React Router, Firebase, Node.js,Express.js,React Bootstrap,React Reveal,Axios,MongoDB, Material UI, Heroku
